divs: sighting detailsi was taking pictures (at dusk) of the landscape in white sands new mexico. at the time of the photos i did not notice anything out of the ordinary, but when i got home and reviewed the images i noticed objects that were unidentifiable. i took three photos of the same scene, my camera (a nikon d70) was on a tripod and very stationary. i have marked the areas where the objects are\were for each of the three frames. the green circles are where the objects are in the first frame, the blue circles are where the objects are in the second fram, and the orange circles are where the objects are in the third frame. the photos\frames were taken within one minute of each other.
Summary: Anomolous objects found after reviewing photos
